# Input Field Styling

All editable input fields (text, date, select, textarea) must use a consistent colour scheme across every view.

- **Text colour**: `#222` (black)
- **Background**: `#f5f5fa` (near-white with a subtle cool tint)
- **Border**: `1px solid #222`
- **Border radius**: `4px`
- **Font size**: `0.9rem` for detail/edit fields, `0.85rem` for filter fields

This applies to:
- Filter bar inputs
- Detail view edit inputs
- Any form inputs for data entry

```css
.some-input {
  color: #222;
  background: #f5f5fa;
  border: 1px solid #222;
  border-radius: 4px;
  color-scheme: dark;
}
```

Never use dark backgrounds or light text colours for input fields.
